incase if source schema is changed(addition of column) then pipeline will fail because schema evolution exception , in that case we need to add retry option for our job in databricks gui

and source sends a new column, Auto Loader usually behaves like this:

Auto Loader detects the new column.
Auto Loader updates the schema in cloudFiles.schemaLocation.
The streaming query fails once with an exception like UnknownFieldException.
On restart/retry, Auto Loader uses the updated schema and continues successfully. Databricks documents this behavior: when Auto Loader evolves schema automatically, the stream initially fails and the evolved schema is used after restart

incase if we get duplicate in landing zone file with different path, then autoloader will consider as new files, In that scenario we can use hashkey
